FBIS3-8651 "dreeu049_b_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 BULGARIA Berov Stable After Heart Surgery AU1103180594 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1700 GMT 11 Mar 94 AU1103180594 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Council of Ministers Press Center has announced that according to information supplied by the medical team treating Prime Minister Lyuben Berov, the team made an extended visit to their patient at about 1800 hours this afternoon, with the surgeons Prof. Levi and Docent Mishev also in attendance. After a five-hour operation, the prime minister is in a stable condition. It was established that all internal organs were operating normally and that the patient's blood pressure was also normal.
